        "cooked": "<p>it was great to see you on Friday! had a blast discussing this, that and any other thing.</p>\n<p>wine is about sharing and the pleasure of trying each and every bottle with great company. Six of us thought it was corked, obviously you derived more pleasure from this bottle and got to enjoy (practically) the entire bottle.</p>\n<p>ps the Lorraine the next night was a \u201creal\u201d pleasure</p>",
